27.000Z","msg":"你指<br />\n<br />\n香港配音fans = 香港聲優fans<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n粵語撚 = TVB 配音fans<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b350455c39e2959b13aeaac9536f8afe085c2611","tid":2372503,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T17:48:12.000Z","msg":"上面提到 永井一郎<br />\n<br />\n就不得不貼呢篇長文：<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">補充材料2：關於永井一郎這個人。如果說聲優界中和井上和彥關係最推心置腹的就應改說是永井一郎了吧。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">像疼愛自己兒子一樣疼愛井上的永井一郎卻因為26多年前的一件聲優界巨變，曾一度和井上的斷交。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">這件事情也使得「青二」開山元老級人物永井一郎對井上和彥產生了極大的不滿，一氣之下與井上斷交長達7年之久，直到日後在為電影『コクーン』的配音工作中相遇又再度續交。永井一郎與井上釋冰，錄制間歇時說的第一句話就是「和彥&hellip;你配的越來越有樣兒了啊&hellip;」，而井上更是感慨萬分的回答「&hellip;原來您還是一直關注著我的啊！」。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">(轉貼)井上和彥介紹</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/home/creationDetail.php?sn=802269\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fhome%2FcreationDetail.php%3Fsn%3D802269&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmemWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=ea64ba8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/home/creationDetail.php?sn=802269</a>"},{"pid":"96830548e9017c9ca487f8d4197b4bf828d34adf","tid":2372503,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0af254162749be9147d66d410619b5d39632f79f","tid":2372503,"uid":25952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T17:31:07.000Z","msg":"佢個等級制度點計？<br />\n點先算一線聲優<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T17:49:29.000Z","msg":"我搵到既資料都係話等級內係15000-45000日元<br />\n每年會評核一次<br />\n<br />\n一線緊係野澤雅子<br />\n至於依家d好鍾意果d，我只可以話係好紅囉<br />\n係唔係一線唔知"},{"pid":"4fe3d677530c12f16fbf59d46cfec94d5e1ad1b7","tid":2372503,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"96830548e9017c9ca487f8d4197b4bf828d34adf","tid":2372503,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":